[%@library file_clock]
[codeblock:synopsis [!:mark UnSpec] ]
namespace std::chrono {
  class file_clock {
  public:
    using rep                       = [$ [:en]a signed arithmetic type[:zh_CN]有符号算术类型];
    using period                    = ratio<[=UnSpec], [=UnSpec]>;
    using duration                  = chrono::duration<rep, period>;
    using time_point                = chrono::time_point<file_clock>;
    static constexpr bool is_steady = [=UnSpec];

    static time_point now() noexcept;

    // [:en] Conversion functions, see below
    // [|:zh_CN] 转换函数，见后文
  };
}
[codeblock:end]

[para]
[:en]
The clock [`file_clock] is used to create the [`time_point] system used for
[`file_time_type] ([#filesystems]).
[:zh_CN]
时钟 [`file_clock] 用于创建用作 [`file_time_type]（[#filesystems]）的
[`time_point] 系统。

[:en]
Its epoch is unspecified.
[:zh_CN]
其纪元是未指明的。
